.SH "NAME"
huge\-split.pl \- Split bigram files from huge\-count.pl into pieces.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
See perldoc huge\-split.pl 
.SH "USAGE"
.IX Header "USAGE"
